-- Balfour Beatty to Sell PFI Stake, Independent on Sunday Reports
-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 2012-04-01T13:27:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/balfour-beatty-to-sell-pfi-stake-independent-on-sunday-reports.html
Balfour Beatty Plc (BBY)  is set to sell
its stake in a Private Finance Initiative scheme, the
 Independent on Sunday  reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Ian Tyler, Balfour’s chief executive officer, is poised to
sell the group’s one-third stake in University College Hospital
in central  London , the newspaper said, without citing sources.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Keith Jenkins  in London at 
 kjenkins3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
